ourVisionFirstText: de_We are a cost and time-effective services provider. One of the reasons we are so efficient is our kickstart formula. Kickstart Formula is 2-4-8, which means 2 days to start; 4 days to gather the requirements; and 8 days to make first prototype.
ourVisionSecondText: de_Our software engineers have over 15 years experience, and for every project we assemble a dedicated team. For clients, this makes us the ideal ‘plug-and-play’ service provider. We collaborate in real-time, and can either work remotely or in client offices. Once you plug Aimit in, we are ready to play with your software

moulkAboutProjectText: de_Our client wanted to start with a minimum viable product (MVP) version of the digital health platform that would allow end users to create orders for Schedule I drugs and laboratory tests. These orders were expected to be delivered directly to a pharmacy or laboratory information system, which could help providers spend less time calling pharmacies and help labs clarify orders and spend more time with patients.
